Interface MoleneModelImplementationI

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BatterySensorModel, ControllerModel, MoleneModel, NetworkModel, PortableComputerModel, PortableComputerStateModel, ServerModel, TicModel, WiFiBandwidthModel, WiFiBandwidthSensorModel, WiFiDisconnectionModel, WiFiModel

    public interface MoleneModelImplementationI
    The interface MoleneModelImplementationI declares methods that all models in the Molene example must implement.

    Description

    Invariant

     invariant              true

    Created on : 2019-12-06

    Author:
    Jacques Malenfant

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Default Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      default void disposePlotters()
      dispose the plotter objects disseminated in the Molene simulation models and that would otherwise persist until a GC pass would collect them; this is useful when several simulation runs are done during the same Java execution.
